   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>This book contains notes of Brother Witness Lee s fellowship with various brothers and sisters.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>The first two chapters were spoken in Manila in June 1959, and the third chapter was given in Taipei in October of the same year.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>All these messages are urgently needed in the churches today.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Hence, they have been collected and are now being published for the rich enjoyment of the saints everywhere.</S>
